<div class="documentation-page">
    <h1>User Manual</h1>
    
    <div class="toc">
        <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#introduction">Introduction</a></li>
            <li><a href="#user-interface">User Interface</a></li>
            <li><a href="#account-management">Account Management</a></li>
            <li><a href="#content-creation">Content Creation</a></li>
            <li><a href="#advanced-features">Advanced Features</a></li>
            <li><a href="#troubleshooting">Troubleshooting</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div id="introduction" class="section">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
            This user manual provides comprehensive information about using the Comserv system.
            It covers all aspects of the platform from basic navigation to advanced features.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div id="user-interface" class="section">
        <h2>User Interface</h2>
        <p>
            The Comserv interface is designed to be intuitive and user-friendly. The main components include:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Navigation Bar</strong>: Located at the top of the screen, provides access to main sections</li>
            <li><strong>Sidebar</strong>: Contains shortcuts to frequently used features</li>
            <li><strong>Main Content Area</strong>: Displays the active content or tool</li>
            <li><strong>Footer</strong>: Contains additional links and information</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div id="account-management" class="section">
        <h2>Account Management</h2>
        <p>
            Managing your account is simple with these tools:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Profile settings</li>
            <li>Password management</li>
            <li>Notification preferences</li>
            <li>Security settings</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div id="content-creation" class="section">
        <h2>Content Creation</h2>
        <p>
            Creating content in Comserv involves these steps:
        </p>
        <ol>
            <li>Navigate to the content section</li>
            <li>Click "Create New" button</li>
            <li>Select the content type</li>
            <li>Fill in the required fields</li>
            <li>Preview your content</li>
            <li>Publish when ready</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    
    <div id="advanced-features" class="section">
        <h2>Advanced Features</h2>
        <p>
            Comserv offers several advanced features for power users:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Workflow automation</li>
            <li>Custom reporting</li>
            <li>API integration</li>
            <li>Batch processing</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div id="troubleshooting" class="section">
        <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
        <p>
            If you encounter issues, try these steps:
        </p>
        <ol>
            <li>Refresh the page</li>
            <li>Clear browser cache</li>
            <li>Check your internet connection</li>
            <li>Verify your permissions</li>
            <li>Contact support if problems persist</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</div>

